[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "ヘルト兄様、いったい何を……？\n料理をしているのか……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01363",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "失敗したときやおかわり用にと、多めに用意していた\n食材を使用して、料理をしているようですね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01364",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ねぇ、ヘルトが作ってる料理って……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01365",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "……ヘルトがあのスープを作ってくれるのは、\nいつも決まって、僕たちが落ち込んでるときだった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01366",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "特訓と称して自ら僕たちを痛めつけるくせに、僕たちが\n沈んでいるのを見ると、励ますかのように作るんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01367",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "じゃあ、今、ヘルトがスープを作ってるのって……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01368",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "兄様……なんだか、手付きがたどたどしいような……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01369",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "はい。どこかおぼつかない様子を受けます。\nやはり、まだ意識がはっきりしていないのでしょう……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01370",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "危ないっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01371",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "……あー、もうっ！　見てらんない！\n僕も手伝うから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01372",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "あ、ありがとう、兄貴……\n温かい……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01373",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "これ……この味だよ、ヘル兄のスープは。\nみんなで作ったのも美味しかったけれど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01374",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "兄者……兄者ぁ……\n兄者のスープじゃあ……！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01375",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "兄者ぁ！　兄者がこのままなんて、我は嫌じゃあ！\n元に戻ってくれ、兄者ぁ～～～！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01376",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "ゼロ姉上が、泣いている……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_01377",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "ゼロ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_01378",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "あ、兄者！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01379",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "……もう、俺は必要ないだろう。\n俺がいなくとも、お前たちは――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_01380",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "嫌じゃ！　必要とか、必要ないとかじゃなく、\n兄者がいないのは嫌じゃあ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01381",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "そうだよ、ヘル兄",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01382",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "アタシたちがヘル兄に勝ったからといって、お前さんが\nアタシたちの兄じゃなくなるわけじゃないんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01383",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "中途半端に役目を放棄して逃げて……ヘルトのせいで\n果ての大陸へたどり着けなかったら許さないし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01384",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "兄様、悩みがあるなら、私たちに教えてください！\n兄弟として、ヘルト兄様の力になりたいです！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01385",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "イェルカ、シトリン、ゴゥ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_01386",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "私たちは知っています。\nヘルト兄様の、私たちに対する優しさと、愛情を",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01387",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "ヘルト兄上は我が主らの命令を聞きませんが、\n私たち兄弟のことは一等大切に思ってくださっている",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_01388",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "怖いこともあるけど、それもこれも、\n私たちのためを思ってくれてたんだよね……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01389",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "リーベ、ヤドヴィガ、キューン……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_01390",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "私には、記憶がないけれど、\nそれでも、みんなから話を聞いて分かった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01391",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "私たち兄弟には、私たちを気にかけてくれる\nヘルトっていう大切なお兄ちゃんがいるってこと！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01392",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "ヴァレリア……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_037_01393",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "これ、私たちみんなで、ヘルトのために作ったの。\n兄弟の愛情たっぷりよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01394",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あんたが私たちのためにスープを作ってくれるように、\n私たちも、ヘルトが辛いときは支えたいの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01395",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "兄者、食べてくれ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01396",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "兄貴……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_01397",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "リーベ",
		"romanized_name": "Liebe",
		"model_path_hash": "281475164831455342",
		"text": "お口に合いませんでしたか……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_156_037_01398",
		"still_path_hash": "5075029600051949533",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "えっ、ちょっと、ヘルト！？\nどこ行くのよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01399",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "……意味分からないんだけど、なんなのあいつ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_01400",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "ゴゥ",
		"romanized_name": "Gou",
		"model_path_hash": "5559160385657202980",
		"text": "な、何か、兄様の気に障ることを\nしてしまったのでしょうか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_155_037_01401",
		"still_path_hash": "2242265198409136417",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "あ、兄者ぁ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_037_01402",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "ゼロ姉上、泣かないでください",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_01403",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "……ヘル兄は、スープを飲んで確かに回復してた。\nアタシたちの想いは、届いているはずさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_01404",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……ヘルト……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_01405",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]